---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Dirty Rabbit" lang="en">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-typewriter text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-lg text-black/60 mb-12">How we handle your data (spoiler: with respect).</p>
      
      <div class="font-mono text-black/80 space-y-8 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">Who is responsible for your data?</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Company:</strong> The Rabbit Project SL</li>
            <li><strong>Tax ID:</strong> B01589308</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> Avda. Platja d'Aro, 275 - Local 2, 17248 S'Agaró, Girona, Spain</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> hola@dirtyrabbit.es</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">What data do we collect?</h2>
          <p>Very little:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Newsletter:</strong> Just your email, if you choose to subscribe</li>
            <li><strong>Contact:</strong> What you write to us via email or form</li>
            <li><strong>Browsing:</strong> Basic technical data (functional cookies)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">We don't sell coffee online, so we don't have payment data or shipping addresses.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">What do we use your data for?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Sending you our newsletter (if you subscribe)</li>
            <li>Responding when you contact us</li>
            <li>Improving the website (anonymous statistics)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Legal basis: your consent when you subscribe or contact us, and our legitimate interest in improving our service.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">How long do we keep your data?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Newsletter:</strong> Until you unsubscribe</li>
            <li><strong>Contact:</strong> As long as needed to resolve your inquiry</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Maximum 12 months</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">Do we share your data?</h2>
          <p>We don't sell or share your data with third parties, except:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Technical providers we need (hosting, email)</li>
            <li>If required by law</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Our providers comply with GDPR.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">Your rights</h2>
          <p>You can exercise your rights to access, rectification, erasure, portability, restriction, and objection by writing to <strong>hola@dirtyrabbit.es</strong>.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">You can also file a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD) if you believe we haven't handled your data correctly.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use technical cookies necessary for the website to function. We don't use advertising or third-party tracking cookies.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">You can configure your browser to reject cookies, though some features might not work properly.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">Security</h2>
          <p>We protect your data with appropriate technical and organizational measures. The website uses HTTPS so all information travels encrypted.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-typewriter text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-red">Changes</h2>
          <p>If we update this policy, we'll publish it here. We recommend checking it from time to time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-black/10">
          <p class="text-black/50">Last updated: February 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
